          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Active sample - a 4He filling of ionization chamber",
                "MUSIC was used as a target. The pressure in the",
                "chamber was 403/395 torr of 4He"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The data were measured using a multisampling",
                "ionization chamber (MUSIC) detector with a close to",
                "100% detection efficiency. Electrons from the",
                "ionization of the gas molecules generated by the",
                "beam particles and evaporation residues as they travel",
                "through the chamber volume, drift pass through the",
                "Frisch grid towards the anode. A segmented anode",
                "allows the investigation of a large part of an",
                "excitation function with a single measurement"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Inverse kinematics was used"
